issue.title: Fix invalid logic in MKLDNN EP that ran past end of nodes and double increment.

issue.body:
**Description**: 
Fix logic where iteration continued past end of valid nodes.
Fix double increment.

**Motivation and Context**
Changes to the optimizers in https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/pull/1407 triggered the iteration bug. Noticed incorrect double increment when fixing it.
